Is this a sign from Dog?

content:
Before we kill another child
for righteousness' sake, to serve
some blissful killer's sacred cause,
some bloody patriot's anthem
and his flag, let us leave forever
our ancestral lands, our holy books,
our god thoughtified to the mean
of our smallest selves. Let us go
to the graveyard and lie down
forever among the speechless stones.

‚Äî Wendell Berry

content:
Naraka Bladepoint gets frame generation today on Nvidia‚Äôs RTX 40 GPUs.

The DLSS 3.0 technique arrives today to dramatically increase perceived framerate by imagining lots of new frames, and the the speedy Naraka‚Äôs a good candidate ‚Äî particularly since it already has Nvidia Reflex to soften the blow to latency. It‚Äôs part of a new GeForce driver today. AMD‚Äôs got similar tech, but also some catching up to do.
